    {
      "id": "28fe4501-0c0e-4f10-ba51-521464c6f6f1",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "#### Conditional Logic\nExplore `if-else` and `switch` expresssions below.",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "28fe4501-0c0e-4f10-ba51-521464c6f6f1"
      }
